commit.message:
Wip Qt 6 port (#337)

* WIP Qt6 port

- Update project version and dependencies
- Update generaded CMake config template

* Replace qAsConst() with std::as_const

* Replace Q_PID with qint64

Q_PID is removed in Qt6

* TODO: Port QRegExp to QRegularExpression

- TODO: check if new syntax is equivalent

* Use QLibraryInfo::path()

In Qt6 QLibraryInfo::location() is deprecated

* SingleApplication: fix KWindowInfo include

- Fix NET namespace

* QWidget::enterEvent() now has QEnterEvent argument

* Use QLayout::setContentsMargins()

QLayout::setMargin() got removed in Qt6

* ScreenSaver: remove QX11Info

- Use QNativeInterface::QX11Application
- Emit warning on Wayland platform which is currently unimplemented

* Use QMouseEvent::globalPosition()

In Qt6 globalPos() is deprecated

* Signal connections: use context QObject

- SingleApplication: exit() is static

* PluginInfo: do not ignore QTranslator::load() return value

* ConfigDialogPrivate: forward declare QWidget

* PluginInfo: export QDebug operators

Previously there was a link error when building `lxqt-panel` project.

Also inline overload taking pointers.

* Remove "2" in lxqt-config.cmake.in

* Fix const regexp. TODO squash with previous commit

commit.message:
Consider LXQt theme names case-insensitively (#308)

`lxqt-config` may also need a small change, but this PR ignores the letter case in the value of `lxqt.conf` → General → theme.

Closes https://github.com/lxqt/lxqt-themes/issues/69
